item.title: CVE-2021-45729|2024-08-04T04:47:02.106Z -- wp%20google%20map -- wp%20google%20map%20%28wordpress%20plugin%29
item.description: The Privilege Escalation vulnerability discovered in the WP Google Map WordPress plugin (versions <= 1.8.0) allows authenticated low-role users to create, edit, and delete maps.
